    "110673561": {
      "title": "The future of PID control",
      "abstract": "Abstract This paper is the last part of a sequence of three plenary papers that cover the past, the present and the future of PID control. It treats specifications, stability, design, applications, and performance of PID control. The paper ends with a discussion about the future of the PID controller."
